Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:02.15,warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻译： 雨意  天井  影子   校译 : 影子  时间/后期 : 岚酱  压制: 茶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说那小鬼是受里见大人照顾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有他在的地方 一定没有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你这孩子终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都睡了一周了 也该醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是 真是让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章彦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着的时候 葬礼已经举行过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章彦明明前一天还好好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么异常…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小孩 很难判断他到底是属于哪个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他回到这里的时候 应该已经是那个世界的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你也要当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一下子睡了这么久 可能是受到了影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是信乃的宠物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它？它叫村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我没让它进浴池里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你居然睡了整整一周呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔会昏睡不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是睡了这么久还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服 一周没洗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧好好洗洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃真是个不可思议的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你头上顶着乌鸦 这也叫普通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃 谢谢你找到了章彦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 信乃 我和章彦是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是被神隐的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昏睡时 班级里的女生们告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说仁可是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里特别我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还一直活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计应该是很久以前的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的真实年龄是22岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我6岁的时候在山里失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后 奶奶拜托中大师父找到我的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已经过了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(264,240)}阴暗的胜利感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,22岁还长得这么幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(1040,314)}根本没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HEFEDF2&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(970,482)}漂亮助攻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉赢得太爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp15\c&H000301&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\frz1.244\pos(624,584)\fad(300,0)}其实是18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说我被找到时 仍然保持6岁的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不记得发生过什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我也不怎么在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了这里之后 我也正常的成长起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 十年后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 信乃的身高早晚也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是防天狗的结界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处都有 还真是夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说仁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他有和我们完全一样的痣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他珠子的主人也有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那珠子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注: 日语中 珠子和蛋蛋同音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦 当然是有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是男孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再确认一次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是第几张了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔 你在这里干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次你进出这里 结界就会被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发牢骚的时间 还不如换上强力结界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…我已经给仁更强的护符了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经回来过的孩子 还有可能再被带走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就相传那座山上住着天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁去那边待得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它喜欢这种人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的父亲不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母亲生下他后 是瞒着村民将他幽禁起来抚养的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是16年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然找到了从悬崖跌落身亡的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从那以后 仁就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年后 我来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从它手里救回仁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把仁在那边时的记忆封印起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它毕竟抚养仁长大 就好像父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父母的话 早晚会来把孩子带回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算找到那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 6年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是7年了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明近在眼前 却费事地找了这么多年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你差不多也该厌倦这自在随意的人世了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 我要找个人收养你这个拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…我…妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 跟我走就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:10:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 好疼啊 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了 什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你已经不是人类的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该早就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚会来把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人类的孩子 把仁还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是曾经被人类抛弃过的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经是我们的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回我们的孩子是父母的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 栲婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我的锡杖在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我顺着气味追过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我这次一定要灭了那只天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月 突然把这家伙带回来 到底想怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可不是阿猫阿狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 别这么无礼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖真乖 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 不是我说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子一眨眼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把一半的命给了这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托叶月 和我一起保护这个孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再让这个孩子孤独一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 你一直这么年幼弱小也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子很美好 孩子就应该被疼爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远都是孩子的摸样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月 华月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月 华月呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有觉得我们一直在刚刚的地方打转？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始 好像就是山神的领域了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 这个结界能破坏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有庄介 想死你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是猎妖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那只天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但遗憾的是 他不是我要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就别来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓 但是对那个孩子来说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许在那边的生活才是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便告诉你个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主即将醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可能集齐八颗明珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 把珠子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 什么都不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再挨饿 也不必再流血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不会再让你孤独一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了 所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 我死了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我之所以还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为华月给了我一半的命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他全心全意地在山上抚养我长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但华月却因我而死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为自从华月把一半的命给了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年来 他已经用尽了作为天狗的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是华月本人所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我也不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 从那么高的悬崖摔下来你居然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没想到会被你们救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是我一生的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠我一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中大法师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还连累你受这样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是栲婆婆的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那个天狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我的伤痊愈后 就立刻去夺回仁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 已经对仁半放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何时这一天终会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那孩子是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是什么话啊 你不疼爱外孙了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 那可是我唯一的外孙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么突然说那种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿曾经寄过一封信给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信上说「我怀了天狗的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我当时没有相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我女儿一直活得很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想肯定是难以启齿的对象的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没和外孙见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在女儿死后 我后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会对那两人置之不理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么说仁真的流淌着天狗的血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你想起我们了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 华月死了的事也想起来了 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个没用的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确说来 大哥并没有真正死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万幸 华月的躯体得以保留
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 有一点我要说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你说想把「半身」还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月也绝不会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的半身 将赠予这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来一切都进行得很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 你以为本大爷是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 快把华月的身体还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我还什么好处都没拿到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我很为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个珠子还是什么的玩意儿 仁手上就有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抢还是要偷 随你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你都这样说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月不在 你们也很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是仁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庄介先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不是他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想见那只天狗的躯壳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你说想把「半身」还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月也绝不会接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然叶月那样说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我却不应该接受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我当时却只是个一无所知的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华月 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是仁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的 他还只是不完全品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话 也只是个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的「半身」给你了吧 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你只要把得到的东西还回去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你带我回来 叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会还给华月应还之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你不要捣乱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.13,0:21:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.81,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:06.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}一人にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:06.06,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}不要让我孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:09.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甘く　甘く色をとって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:09.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}甜美地 绽放色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:13.24,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.57,0:22:13.24,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要轻易离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:17.62,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕の命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:17.62,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你就是我的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:24.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どうしてねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:24.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:29.80,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}どうして君の願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:29.80,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底是为什么 你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:35.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみの雨に打たれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:35.13,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}虽被悲伤之雨淋透
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:36.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}咲いてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:36.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却依旧傲然怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:44.02,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう大事なもの傷つけたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:44.02,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}已经不能伤害重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.52,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その静かな笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.52,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只想默默守候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:52.28,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ守りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.52,0:22:52.28,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你那恬静的笑颜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:56.11,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その手を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:56.11,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}伸出你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:59.66,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独さえ壊すほどに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:59.66,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}去打破孤寂的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.79,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終焉の時も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:02.79,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直到终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君がいるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:05.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要有你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:07.38,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:07.38,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我就不会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:10.75,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君は僕を照らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.38,0:23:10.75,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只有你能照亮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:15.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}ただ一つの光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:15.84,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,900)}是我唯一的光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次见到信乃的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为转来了一位超可爱的女孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是听说你实际上已经18岁时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得什么啊根本不足畏惧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.55,0:23:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 一脸笑嘻嘻的是在找揍吗
